  "text": "It is well known that superfield supergravity action is given by the volume of the superspace [CITATION_1] , this is to say by integral over the curved supergravity superspace Σ (4|4) of the Berezenian (superdeterminant) E := sdet(E A M ) of the supervielbein E A M (Z),",
